Key Match Events: Jamie Leweling scored the winner in the 64th minute
Pre-Game Insights: Germany held a farewell tribute for Ilkay Gündogan, Manuel Neuer, Thomas Müller and Toni Kroos following their retirements from international football
Post-Match Reflections: Jamie Leweling: 'We won as a team. I scored but we played a good game and I am happy to have helped'
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Dutch were missing Virgil van Dijk through suspension
Others: Germany are top of Group A3 with 10 points from four matches and are guaranteed a spot in the next round
